{
  "texts": [
    "Why Text Summarization and Explainable AI(XAI)?",
    "An explanation is an attempt at extracting useful, concise information from a complex, black-box model.",
    "Likewise a summary attempts to extract the essential bits of a longer piece of text.",
    "Seen this way, an explanation summarizes the model's prediction, and a summary explains the summarized piece of text.",
    "It is thus beneficial to consider the two problems together since approaches to one can inform the approaches to the other, as we will provide examples throughout the survey."
  ]
}